<li>1989 with <a href="/wiki/Mark_Turner_(cognitive_scientist)" title="Mark Turner (cognitive scientist)">Mark Turner</a>. <i>More Than Cool Reason: A Field Guide to Poetic Metaphor</i>. University of Chicago Press.</li>
